OL,3,CConcerns raised over hospital care of
OL,4,Cex-footballer Kevin Campbell
OL,6,FConcerns over the hospital care of
OL,7,Fformer Arsenal and Everton footballer
OL,8,FKevin Campbell have been flagged up by
OL,9,Fa health trust, an inquest has heard.
OL,11,FMr Campbell died at the age of 54 at
OL,12,FManchester Royal Infirmary (MRI) on 15
OL,13,FJune after he was admitted there a
OL,14,Fmonth earlier.
