OL,3,CConcerns raised over hospital care of
OL,4,Cex-footballer Kevin Campbell
OL,6,FOpening an inquest into his death, on
OL,7,FThursday 4 July, Zak Golombek, area
OL,8,Fcoroner for Manchester, said
OL,9,FManchester University NHS Foundation
OL,10,FTrust, which manages the hospital, had
OL,11,Fdeclared a Level 5 patient safety
OL,12,Fincident ` the most serious category `
OL,13,Fabout aspects of his care.
OL,15,FHe said the provisional cause of death
OL,16,Fgiven for Mr Campbell was multi-organ
OL,17,Ffailure due to a heart infection.
OL,19,FNo family members were present at
OL,20,FManchester Coroner's Court as Mr
OL,21,FGolombek outlined background details.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
