OL,3,CConcerns raised over hospital care of
OL,4,Cex-footballer Kevin Campbell
OL,6,FMr Golombek said: "In terms of the
OL,7,Fcircumstances of his death he had been
OL,8,Fadmitted to Manchester Royal Infirmary
OL,9,Fon 15 May 2024.
OL,11,F"He had been reported to have been fit
OL,12,Fand well until around January 2024
OL,13,Fwhen he had a number of admissions to
OL,14,Fhospital before this final admission.
OL,26,@nD@SOUsD@AOU
