OL,3,CConcerns raised over hospital care of
OL,4,Cex-footballer Kevin Campbell
OL,6,F"I have been notified that Manchester
OL,7,FUniversity NHS Foundation Trust which
OL,8,Fmanages Manchester Royal Infirmary has
OL,9,Fdeclared a Level 5 incident related to
OL,10,Faspects of Mr Campbell's care in which
OL,11,Fthere is reference to both a delay in
OL,12,Faspects of his care and diagnosis, and
OL,13,Falso concerns raised over decision-
OL,14,Fmaking processes with regards to the
OL,15,Finstitutions of palliative care.
OL,17,F"Those matters are now subject to
OL,18,Finternal investigations by the
OL,19,Fhospital trust.
OL,26,@nD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
