OL,3,CConcerns raised over hospital care of
OL,4,Cex-footballer Kevin Campbell
OL,6,F"Therefore I am able to direct that
OL,7,Fthere should be additional evidence to
OL,8,Fbe obtained which includes the
OL,9,Finvestigation report, together with
OL,10,Fassociated witness statements from all
OL,11,Frelevant clinicians involved in Mr
OL,12,FCampbell's care and also a statement
OL,13,Fbe obtained from Mr Campbell's next of
OL,14,Fkin in order to provide an antecedent
OL,15,Fhistory for Mr Campbell and to set out
OL,16,Fany concerns that the family may have
OL,17,Fhad in relation to his care.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
