OL,3,CConcerns raised over hospital care of
OL,4,Cex-footballer Kevin Campbell
OL,6,F"I have also received notification
OL,7,Ffrom the trust that a medical cause of
OL,8,Fdeath can be offered and therefore I
OL,9,Fwill consider evidence from the
OL,10,Fclinicians involved in Mr Campbell's
OL,11,Fcare as to the cause of his death.
OL,13,F"The provisional cause of death, as it
OL,14,Fstands, refers to Mr Campbell dying
OL,15,Ffrom multi-organ failure as a result
OL,16,Fof infective endocarditis.
OL,18,F"So, final determinations on the
OL,19,Fmedical cause of death and the care
OL,20,Fafforded to Mr Campbell will be made
OL,21,Fas part of the inquest process.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
