OL,3,CConcerns raised over hospital care of
OL,4,Cex-footballer Kevin Campbell
OL,6,F"I will adjourn the proceedings to
OL,7,Fawait additional disclosure."
OL,9,FNo date was set for a further hearing.
OL,11,FAccording to the NHS website,
OL,12,Fendocarditis is a rare and potentially
OL,13,Ffatal infection of the inner lining of
OL,14,Fthe heart and is most commonly caused
OL,15,Fby bacteria entering the blood and
OL,16,Ftravelling to the heart.
